---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section class="events" data-events>
  <img class="events__bg" src={`${base}Images/events3.jpg`} alt="" />
  <div class="events__dim"></div>

  <div class="events__layout">
    <div class="events__header">
      <div class="events__title-wrap">
        <span class="events__title-outline">XR</span>
        <h2 class="events__title">Events</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="events__body">
      <div class="events__desc-wrap">
        <p class="events__desc">The XR Club hosts several events throughout the year and often partners with major student organizations. Our flagship event is our project demo presentation, where teams showcase their work. We're also in the middle of organizing a hackathon in partnership with IXA Alliance.</p>
        <p class="events__desc">Past highlights include Mini Demo Day, TerpCon 2026, KAMECON 2026, and the UMD Gaming LAN. We also run workshops and occasional Beat Saber tournaments. <strong>Join our Discord to stay updated on upcoming events!</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="events__kickoff">
        <img src={`${base}Images/kickoff.png`} alt="XR Club Kickoff" class="events__kickoff-img" />
        <p class="events__kickoff-caption">Ever wanted to work on real XR projects, meet people building wild things, and join a community doing it all at once? Come to our XR Club Kickoff.</p>
        <p class="events__kickoff-caption">It's our only info session of the year, featuring a live project symposium across VR, AR, spatial computing, BCIs, and more, plus major announcements, new partnerships, and upcoming opportunities. Network with the teams behind it all and find where you want to jump in.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="events__collage">
      <div class="events__photo events__photo--a"><img src={`${base}Images/events1.jpg`} alt="XR Club event" /></div>
      <div class="events__photo events__photo--b"><img src={`${base}Images/events2.jpg`} alt="XR Club event" /></div>
      <div class="events__photo events__photo--c"><img src={`${base}Images/events4.jpg`} alt="XR Club event" /></div>
      <div class="events__photo events__photo--d"><img src={`${base}Images/events7.jpg`} alt="XR Club event" /></div>
      <div class="events__photo events__photo--e"><img src={`${base}Images/events5.jpg`} alt="XR Club event" /></div>
      <div class="events__photo events__photo--f"><img src={`${base}Images/events3.jpg`} alt="XR Club event" /></div>
      <div class="events__photo events__photo--g"><img src={`${base}Images/events6.jpg`} alt="XR Club event" /></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .events {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    visibility: hidden;
  }

  .events::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 120px;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95), transparent);
    z-index: 3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .events::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 120px;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95));
    z-index: 3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .events__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .events__dim {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .events__layout {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 4;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    padding: 5.5rem var(--page-padding) 3rem;
    gap: 1rem;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .events__header {
    text-align: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .events__title-wrap {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .events__title-outline {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(8rem, 14vw, 15rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1.5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .events__title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 9vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 0.9;
    text-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
  }

  .events__body {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .events__desc-wrap {
    max-width: 480px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .events__desc {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.82rem, 0.95vw, 0.95rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .events__desc:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .events__desc strong {
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .events__kickoff {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    max-width: 20rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .events__kickoff-img {
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 10rem;
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: 0.625rem;
  }

  .events__kickoff-caption {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.68rem, 0.8vw, 0.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    line-height: 1.55;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .events__collage {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .events__photo {
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 0;
  }

  .events__photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 400ms ease;
  }

  .events__photo:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .events__photo--a { grid-column: 1 / 5;   grid-row: 1; }
  .events__photo--b { grid-column: 5 / 9;   grid-row: 1; }
  .events__photo--c { grid-column: 9 / 13;  grid-row: 1; }

  .events__photo--d { grid-column: 1 / 4;   grid-row: 2; }
  .events__photo--e { grid-column: 4 / 7;   grid-row: 2; }
  .events__photo--f { grid-column: 7 / 10;  grid-row: 2; }
  .events__photo--g { grid-column: 10 / 13; grid-row: 2; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .events__title-outline { font-size: 6rem; }
    .events__title { font-size: 3.5rem; }

    .events__body {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }

    .events__desc-wrap {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .events__kickoff-img {
      max-height: 18vh;
    }

    .events__collage {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .events__photo--a { grid-column: 1 / 3; grid-row: 1; }
    .events__photo--b { grid-column: 3 / 5; grid-row: 1; }
    .events__photo--c { grid-column: 5 / 7; grid-row: 1; }
    .events__photo--d { grid-column: 1 / 3; grid-row: 2; }
    .events__photo--e { grid-column: 3 / 5; grid-row: 2; }
    .events__photo--f { grid-column: 5 / 7; grid-row: 2; }
    .events__photo--g { display: none; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .events__layout { padding: 4rem 1rem 2.5rem; }
    .events__title-outline { font-size: 4.5rem; }
    .events__title { font-size: 2.5rem; }

    .events__kickoff-img {
      max-height: 14vh;
    }

    .events__collage {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .events__photo--a { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 1; }
    .events__photo--b { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 1; }
    .events__photo--c { grid-column: 1; grid-row: 2; }
    .events__photo--d { grid-column: 2; grid-row: 2; }
    .events__photo--e { display: none; }
    .events__photo--f { display: none; }
    .events__photo--g { display: none; }
  }
</style>
